  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Patients with colon cancer or upper aero-digestive tract and candidates for treatment with
        cetuximab
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient informed consent,

          -  Patient aged over 18 years

          -  Patients with a WHO performance status ≤ 2,

          -  Colon cancer or upper aero-digestive tract cytologically or histologically proven

          -  Patients with an indication to the theoretical use of cetuximab for colon neoplasia or
             upper aero-digestive tract,

          -  Haematological and biochemical compatible with combination therapy with cetuximab.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients previously treated with cetuximab,

          -  A person deprived of liberty or under supervision.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
